    <h2>The Red Panda</h2>
    <p>The Red Panda is a cat-size mammal originally from southwestern China. It
      has reddish-brown fur and a long, bushy tail. Red pandas primarily eat
      bamboo, but are considered carnivorous as they also eat eggs, birds, and
      insects.</p>
    <span>Other names: Fire Fox, Red Bear-Cat</span>
